{"tid":818940,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"教女朋友用電話教到好燥","createTime":"2018-09-14T12:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T19:48:04.000Z","uid":12618,"like":26,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3e49c78d129898389cb18bab794d1719c18b4d","tid":818940,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"琴日女朋友終於出左部iphone8<br />\n佢第一次用蘋果野好多都唔識<br />\n今日就黎料<br />\n我用左幾年iphone佢有問題自然問我<br />\n佢話想入歌入相<br />\n我咪講左iTunes 同itools比佢囉<br />\n講左一大輪 話iTunes入相就麻煩啲要開file導入<br />\niTools 就唔洗直接拉入去就得<br />\n我提議佢用iTools 因為容易啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話電腦無反應<br />\n我話無可能  問佢電腦果度連部電話既資料都無顯示？<br />\n佢話無<br />\n最後我問係咪無插線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話乜要插線架？<br />\n我話唔插線點入野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣已經燥燥地<br />\n<br />\n插完之後佢等左五分鐘都話仲係無反應<br />\n原來佢自己岸鳩無係電話度撳確定連電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢問點入歌  我話上面果行制揀返音樂<br />\n佢問係咪要導入<br />\n我扯撚左火 即刻開佢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係無聽書  直接拉入去就得啦導咩入姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你知唔知要導入係邊個程式<br />\n原來我一開始咁解釋iTunes itools都係廢話<br />\n<br />\n佢又嘈我話係咪唔答點入歌<br />\n我話係乜野都唔識又唔上網睇左先學咩人買iphone  <br />\n教完你仲發我脾氣 過橋抽板<br />\n嬲嬲地唔開po唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd7d123d065ac30d6ea7c47175fe6625ce29ab2","tid":818940,"uid":2950,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"最後我問係咪無插線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話乜要插線架？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2409facf61963b65e3d9cdc1bb7989f6a0b197c","tid":818940,"uid":140573,"like":3