 />\n插完之後佢等左五分鐘都話仲係無反應<br />\n原來佢自己岸鳩無係電話度撳確定連電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢問點入歌  我話上面果行制揀返音樂<br />\n佢問係咪要導入<br />\n我扯撚左火 即刻開佢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係無聽書  直接拉入去就得啦導咩入姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你知唔知要導入係邊個程式<br />\n原來我一開始咁解釋iTunes itools都係廢話<br />\n<br />\n佢又嘈我話係咪唔答點入歌<br />\n我話係乜野都唔識又唔上網睇左先學咩人買iphone  <br />\n教完你仲發我脾氣 過橋抽板<br />\n嬲嬲地唔開po唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"嗰個唔喺你條女，喺你老母<br />\n樓豬醒下啦吊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed95df0bbf17670c1663da2c1b5d0ce77daebf7d","tid":818940,"uid":7805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"煲老藕曬鬼曬馬咩<br />\n又係棋靈王啲frd"},{"pid":"f76f030042c05f5a7fa0e3169f14141f10cdcba2","tid":818940,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:42:34.000Z","msg":"想屌西就唔好咁多抱怨"},{"pid":"cbe0b468818c2221759904b6a1ed57aded07e620","tid":818940,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"ios太封閉"},{"pid":"161b1bdfc2b32fe831fa13d92c0867e8efb622c0","tid":818940,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T14:23:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69e3a465f1c3385e116d148ab90297f042aa0d09","tid":818940,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed95df0bbf17670c1663da2c1b5d0ce77daebf7d","tid":818940,"uid":7805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"煲老藕曬鬼曬馬咩<br />\n又係棋靈王啲frd"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"鮑姐不了"},{"pid":"4e79848fb6e5244125fce8529f95071990ca100e","tid":818940,"uid":52683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"Pass俾我教都得 利申4年使用ios經驗<img src=\"/assets/fac